            "heading": "",
            "body": "Versatile and timeless, the Flare Café Chair comes in finishes that complement a wide range of environments. Its durable construction ensures everyday reliability while maintaining a refined, modern look. Built for both comfort and practicality, it adapts seamlessly to dynamic, multifunctional spaces."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "The backrest features a hand-woven cane insert framed in solid wood, providing breathable support with timeless craftsmanship. Its open weave enhances airflow for added comfort, while the sturdy wooden frame ensures stability and a warm, elegant aesthetic."
          },
